    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "SUBJECT: FLYING SAUCERS INTERNATIONAL,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "OFFICIAL JOURNAL OF THE",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "AMALGAMATED FLYING SAUCER",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "CLUBS OF AMERICA, INC.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "IS - MISCELLANEOUS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "O FLYING SAUCERS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "The Philadelphia Division by letter dated 9/22/66,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "furnished the Los Angeles Division with Issue No. 24 dated",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "July, 1966, entitled \"FLYING SAUCERS INTERNATIONAL\", which is",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "the official journal of the Amalgamated Flying Saucer Clubs",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "of America, Inc. The Philadelphia Division received the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "magazine from Mr. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "Philadelphia, Pennsylvania on 9/19/66. Mr. [REDACTED] stated he",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "subscribed to the magazine because his son had exhibited an",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "interest in flying saucers and outer space. He said that on",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "pages 2 and 3 of Issue No. 24 was an article which he believed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "expounded the Communist Party (CP) line.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "For the information of the Bureau, the International",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "Headquarters of the Amalgamated Flying Saucer Clubs of America,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "Inc. is located at 2004 North Hoover Street, Los Angeles,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "California. The article, on pages 2 and 3, were allegedly",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "written by Master KALEN-LI RETAN, Head of the planet KORENDOR,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "which was received on 5/4/66 by special directional short-wave",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "radio by BOB RENAUD.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "The indices of the Los Angeles Division contain no",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "information identifiable with RENAUD, and no investigation has",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "ever been conducted on captioned organization. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "No further action is contemplated in this matter",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
